headline: 3 Reasons to Buy Carnival Stock Like There's No Tomorrow
summary: Carnival reported record revenue, operating income, and customer deposits in Q1, highlighting its strong momentum.  There were others, like Carnival (NYSE: CCL), that struggled because operations had to be temporarily shut down for safety concerns.  When Carnival was forced to dock its ships, unsurprisingly, there was no way to service any demand.
